July 28, 2017 9:19 AM ET
Commercial Services and Supplies

Company Overview of The Diana Davis Spencer Foundation



Snapshot People




Company Overview
The Diana Davis Spencer Foundation operates as a non-profit organization that promotes entrepreneurship and free enterprise by supporting healthcare, art, environment, and education sectors. Additionally, the organization provides grants in the field of public policy, global initiatives, and national security. The Diana Davis Spencer Foundation was formerly known as Kathryn W. Davis Foundation. The Diana Davis Spencer Foundation was founded in 2008 and is based in Bethesda, Maryland.


3 Bethesda Metro CenterSuite 118Bethesda, MD 20814United StatesFounded in 2008



Phone: 301-961-4000

www.ddsfoundation.org







